    "created_at": "2017-03-03T00:33:26Z",
    "updated_at": "2017-03-03T00:34:48Z",
    "body": "I'm facing a close behavior: once the modal window is displayed, any attempt to quit the application (through Command+Q or the menu item) close the modal, then the main window is still displayed and would be closed only through the red cross button.\r\n\r\nIMHO, regardless of modal behavior, when I want to quit an application on MacOSX, I use Command+Q and expect it works :smile:."
