    "body": "IMHO - the modal window is asking for an action to be performed, and should not allow quitting the app. please try this in mac:\r\n1. open excel\r\n2. type something\r\n3. now try to save, you will get a modal window,\r\n4. hit command+q\r\nobservation - nothing happens"
